      "span_text": "The terms \"internal relationship marketing\", \"internal relationship management\" or \"internal social management process\" are proposed as an alternative to foreign literature. [CITATION_2] revisited the literature and warns that there is a variety of formats for the implementation of internal market, which confuse and create ambiguity instead of clarity and understanding."
